description:
AJUW-28 EMBROIDERED VISCOSE 3 Pcs

By Pcs: 3 Pcs Shirt: Viscose Trouser: Viscose Dupatta: Viscose Color: Black

Steeped in mystery, this black ensemble is a tapestry of elegance. The heavily embroidered shirt is adorned with intricate threadwork in contrasting hues and gold sequins that gleam like constellations in a dark sky. The printed dupatta drapes like a shadowy veil, adding an enigmatic touch to your look.
DESIGN DETAILS:

Embroidered front center panel on dyed viscose

Embroidered front left/right kali on dyed viscose

1 meter embroidered sleeves on dyed viscose

30 inch embroidered front daman border on dyed viscose

30 inch embroidered back daman border on dyed viscose

30 inch back on dyed viscose

2.5 meter dyed viscose trouser

2.4 meter digital viscose dupatta
